U.S. Sulfur Production, Shipments, Stockpiles for June

-- B y   M i k e   S e b a n y
-- 
2011-09-21T20:16:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/u-s-sulfur-production-shipments-stockpiles-for-june-table-.html
Following is a table detailing U.S.
sulfur production, shipments and stockpiles for June, according
to the  U.S. Geological Survey  in Reston,  Virginia . Sulfur is
used in the preparation of sulfuric acid, which is used to
manufacture chemicals included in fertilizers, paints, detergents
and explosives.  
